Class GroupController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oneops.proxy.web.GroupController

  • @RequestMapping(value="/groups/{appGroup}")
public class GroupController
extends Object
    Keywhiz application group controller. appGroup is the OneOps environment name with {org}_{assembly}_{env} format, for which you are managing the secrets.
